<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n10075e"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10075e">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10075e"> 75(e)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> <font face="wake">D</font> consoler <small>Red</small></blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">J&apos;ouvre le dictionnaire philosophique de Voltaire, au mot de Poste, et j&apos;y trouve: &ldquo;La poste est le lien de toutes les affaires, de toutes les n&eacute;gociations: les absents deviennent par elle pr&eacute;sents; elle est <mark>la consolation</mark> de la vie.&rdquo; <font color="green">[Opening Voltaire&apos;s philosophical dictionary to the word Post, I find &ldquo;The post is the link for all business and all negotiations. Those who are absent are made present by it. It is life&apos;s consolation.&rdquo;]</font> <small> Arthur de Rothschild, <a name="ARHD" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#ARHD"><cite title="source">Histoire de la poste</cite></a> (1876) 8</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Note: See also <a name="n21066c" href="n21all.htm#n21066c">N21 (VI.B.20):066(c)</a> </mm> </dd></dl>
